edia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yesterday I rushed to hospital as I was very unwell with a bug that I am being treated for, and am feeling better now,\\\" Wiffen wrote Sunday on Twitter, sharing he would not be at the Olympics closing ceremony where he was scheduled to be a flag bearer.\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7767931108514837e-16, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks everyone who reached out, I am incredibly disappointed to miss out on the opportunity to be flag bearer last night.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yesterday I rushed to hospital as I was very unwell with a bug that I am being treated for, and am feeling better now.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope everyone enjoys the evening\\u2026  - Daniel Wiffen (@WiffenDaniel)August 12, 2024    The 23-year-oldOlympianswam in thepollutedriverduring the men's 10-kilometer event Friday.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen came in 18th place in his first time swimming in an open-water event.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen won gold in the men's 800-meter freestyle and bronze in the 1500-meter freestyle, which takes place indoors.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's probably one of the worst things I have ever done,\\\" WiffentoldRTE after the event.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But, yeah, I am happy I did it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NANTERRE, FRANCE - JULY 30: Daniel Wiffen of Team Ireland celebrates after winning gold in 